            "id": "4539406",
            "title": "Verano expands revolving credit facility to $100M, extends maturity",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Verano Holdings (VRNO:CA) has <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20365492-verano-announces-agreement-to-upsize-revolving-credit-facility-commitment-to-100000-000-and\">amended</a> its revolving credit facility, increasing commitments from $75M to $100M and extending maturity to February 28, 2029.</li>\n<li>The upsized facility required no additional collateral and remains secured by certain owned real estate.</li>\n<li>$50M has been drawn to date, leaving $50M available subject to certain conditions.</li>\n<li>The amendment enhances Verano’s balance sheet flexibility, supporting lower-cost debt, redraw optionality, and potential release of real estate collateral.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
