            "id": "4539405",
            "title": "Oshkosh Defense wins $53M U.S. army order for Common Bridge Transporters",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li><p data-eci=\"true\">Oshkosh Defense (OSK) has <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20365450-oshkosh-defense-receives-53-million-order-for-common-bridge-transporters-cbt\">received</a> a $53M order from U.S. Army Contracting Command–Detroit Arsenal for Common Bridge Transporters under the Family of Heavy Tactical Vehicle V program.</p></li> <li><p>The Common Bridge Transporter is built on Oshkosh’s heavy tactical truck platform and is designed to support combat mobility in complex terrain and threat environments.</p></li> <li><p>The vehicle enables the transport, launch, and retrieval of bridge bays and bridge erection boats to help maneuver forces cross wet gaps.</p></li> <li><p>The order reinforces Oshkosh Defense’s role as a key supplier of advanced mobility solutions to the U.S. Army.</p></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
